<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-39-1289 </DOCNO><TEXT>The Design Bureau of the Giprokoks research institute developed and testeda system for control of slurry level in tanks of the Ukraina-80 vacuumfilters used for dewatering flotation tailings in coal preparation plants.The SAR automatic level control uses the EhKhO-3 level indicators (whichdetermine slurry level using sound signals that travel in the air abovetailings and are reflected by slurry stored in a tank of vacuum filters).Block scheme of the SAR control system is discussed. Performance testsof experimental units of the SAR system show it to be reliable and accuratefor slurry level control.</TEXT></DOC>